# Svelte Components

- Use Svelte 5 runes: `$state`, `$derived`, `$effect`, `$props`
- Props interface with `interface Props` and `let { ... }: Props = $props()`
- Tailwind classes with `/` (like `bg-surface/50`) cannot be used in `class:` directives — use template string interpolation instead
- Add `aria-` attributes and keyboard handlers for accessibility
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` for animations

```svelte
// ❌ BAD — class: directive breaks on slashes
class:bg-surface/50={condition}

// ✅ GOOD — use string interpolation
class="{condition ? 'bg-brand text-white' : 'bg-surface/50 text-text-secondary'}"
```
